<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us | SCA Marinescu & Associates</title>
  <meta name="description" content="SCA Marinescu & Associates — civil law firm founded in 2006, with over 18 years of experience, legal rigour and strategic vision." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://sca-marinescu.ro/en/about" />
  <link rel="alternate" href="https://sca-marinescu.ro/despre-noi" hreflang="ro-RO" />
  <link rel="alternate" href="https://sca-marinescu.ro/en/about" hreflang="en" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --gold: #C9A55A;
      --dark: #0E0D0C;
      --dark-nav: #131210;
      --off-white: #F0EBE0;
      --gray: #6B6860;
      --gray-light: #9A9590;
      --line: rgba(201, 165, 90, 0.14);
      --nav-h: 130px;
    }

    html, body { min-height: 100%; overflow-x: hidden; }
    html { scroll-padding-top: var(--nav-h); }
    body { font-family: 'Georgia', serif; background: var(--dark); color: var(--off-white); }

    .shell { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2.5rem; }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav#mainNav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 300;
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem; min-height: var(--nav-h);
      background: var(--dark-nav); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .logo { text-decoration: none; flex-shrink: 0; transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1); }
    .logo-image { display: block; height: 98px; width: auto; }
    .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-left: auto; }
    .lang-switch {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.56rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--gold);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,165,90,0.35); padding: 0.45rem 0.7rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, background 0.2s; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .lang-switch:hover { color: var(--off-white); border-color: var(--gold); background: rgba(201,165,90,0.12); }
    .menu-btn-icon { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; gap: 4px; }
    .menu-btn-icon span { display: block; height: 1.5px; background: var(--gold); }
    .menu-btn-icon span:nth-child(1) { width: 22px; }
    .menu-btn-icon span:nth-child(2) { width: 16px; }
    .menu-btn-icon span:nth-child(3) { width: 22px; }
    .menu-btn-label { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 0.3rem; }
    .menu-btn-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; cursor: pointer; background: none; border: none; }

    @media (min-width: 901px) { nav#mainNav.menu-open .logo { transform: translateX(-2rem); } }

    /* ── BACKDROP ── */
    .overlay-backdrop { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 199; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.4s ease; }
    .overlay-backdrop.visible { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }

    /* ── OVERLAY MENU ── */
    .overlay {
      position: fixed; top: 0; right: 0; width: 40%; height: 100vh; z-index: 200;
      background: var(--dark); display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
      overflow-y: auto; overflow-x: hidden; border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .overlay.open { transform: translateX(0); }
    .overlay-top { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; padding: 1.6rem 2rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .close-btn { background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.3rem; color: var(--off-white); transition: color 0.2s; }
    .close-btn:hover { color: var(--gold); }
    .close-btn svg { stroke: currentColor; stroke-width: 1.5; }
    .close-label { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: inherit; }
    .overlay-nav { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start; padding: 1rem 3rem; gap: 0.4rem; }
    .overlay-nav a { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.8vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; color: var(--off-white); line-height: 1.35; transition: color 0.2s; font-family: 'Georgia', serif; }
    .overlay-nav a:hover, .overlay-nav a[aria-current="page"] { color: var(--gold); }
    .overlay-footer { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; flex-shrink: 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,165,90,0.1); }
    .overlay-legal { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.58rem; color: rgba(240,235,224,0.42); letter-spacing: 0.05em; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── PAGE LAYOUT ── */
    .page-wrap { padding-top: var(--nav-h); min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

    .page-header { padding: 3.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }

    .eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.35em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .page-h1 {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.4rem);
      font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--off-white);
    }

    .page-body { flex: 1; }

    .content-section { padding: 3rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .content-section:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 4.5rem; }

    .section-label {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .content-body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(240,235,224,0.75);
      max-width: 760px;
    }
    .content-body p { margin-bottom: 1.3rem; }
    .content-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    /* Values */
    .values-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

    .value-item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2.5rem 1fr; gap: 1.2rem; max-width: 760px; }

    .value-num {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1; padding-top: 0.05rem;
    }

    .value-name {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--off-white); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .value-desc {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(240,235,224,0.62);
    }

    /* Footer */
    .site-footer { background: var(--dark-nav); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 1.5rem 0; }
    .footer-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; }
    .footer-inner p { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: rgba(240,235,224,0.4); }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .footer-links a { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; color: rgba(240,235,224,0.45); transition: color 0.2s; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      :root { --nav-h: 112px; }
      nav#mainNav { padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem; min-height: var(--nav-h); }
      .logo-image { height: 83px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .overlay { width: 100%; border-left: none; }
      .overlay-nav { padding: 1rem 2rem; }
      .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .logo-image { height: 73px; }
      .menu-btn-label { display: none; }
      .shell { padding: 0 1.2rem; }
      .footer-links { gap: 1rem; }
      .value-item { grid-template-columns: 2rem 1fr; gap: 0.8rem; }
    }
    @media (max-height: 700px) and (orientation: landscape) {
      :root { --nav-h: 87px; }
      nav#mainNav { min-height: var(--nav-h); padding-top: 0.6rem; padding-bottom: 0.6rem; }
      .logo-image { height: 68px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="overlay-backdrop" id="overlayBackdrop"></div>

  <div class="overlay" id="overlay" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Main menu">
    <div class="overlay-top">
      <button class="close-btn" id="closeBtn" aria-label="Close menu">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
          <line x1="2" y1="2" x2="20" y2="20"/>
          <line x1="20" y1="2" x2="2" y2="20"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="close-label">Close</span>
      </button>
    </div>
    <nav class="overlay-nav">
      <a href="/en">Home</a>
      <a href="/en/about" aria-current="page">About Us</a>
      <a href="/en/practice-areas">Practice Areas</a>
      <a href="/en/blog">Legal Blog</a>
      <a href="/en/contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <footer class="overlay-footer">
      <div class="overlay-legal">&copy; 2026 Societatea Civilă de Avocatură Marinescu &amp; Associates</div>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <nav id="mainNav">
    <a href="/en" class="logo" aria-label="SCA Marinescu, home page">
      <img src="/company-logo-gold.svg" alt="Marinescu &amp; Associates" class="logo-image" />
    </a>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <a href="/despre-noi" class="lang-switch" hreflang="ro" aria-label="Versiunea în română">RO</a>
      <button class="menu-btn-wrap" id="menuBtn" aria-label="Open menu" aria-expanded="false">
        <div class="menu-btn-icon"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <span class="menu-btn-label">Menu</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="page-wrap">

    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="shell">
        <p class="eyebrow">Civil Law Firm</p>
        <h1 class="page-h1">About Us</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="page-body">

      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="shell">
          <div class="content-body">
            <p>SCA Marinescu &amp; Associates, headquartered in Bucharest, is a civil law firm founded in 2006, defined by continuity, legal rigour and a strategic vision adapted to the dynamics of the administrative and business environment in Romania.</p>
            <p>Under the coordination of attorney Flavius-George Marinescu, our team combines over 18 years of experience at the Bucharest Bar with the multidisciplinary expertise of specialists in niche areas, providing our partners with integrated consulting, assistance and representation solutions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="shell">
          <p class="section-label">Our Values and Client Approach</p>
          <div class="content-body" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
            <p>The reputation of SCA Marinescu &amp; Associates is built on three fundamental pillars:</p>
          </div>
          <div class="values-list">
            <div class="value-item">
              <span class="value-num">1</span>
              <div>
                <p class="value-name">Applied Expertise</p>
                <p class="value-desc">We do not merely offer legal opinions — we deliver pragmatic solutions resulting from an in-depth knowledge of administrative mechanisms from the inside.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="value-item">
              <span class="value-num">2</span>
              <div>
                <p class="value-name">Integrity and Professional Ethics</p>
                <p class="value-desc">Every mandate is managed with the utmost diligence, upholding the ethical standards of the legal profession.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="value-item">
              <span class="value-num">3</span>
              <div>
                <p class="value-name">Long-Term Strategic Vision</p>
                <p class="value-desc">We approach cases through the lens of their future impact, transforming legal risks into opportunities for operational stability.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="shell">
          <p class="section-label">Partnership</p>
          <div class="content-body">
            <p>Through our strategic partnership with the Chamber of Tax Consultants, we offer an integrated approach at the intersection of legal rigour and high-level fiscal expertise.</p>
            <p>SCA Marinescu &amp; Associates assumes the role of trusted legal partner, ensuring elite representation at every procedural stage — from first instance through to extraordinary appeals — thereby guaranteeing complete protection of your interests.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="shell">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Societatea Civilă de Avocatură Marinescu &amp; Associates</p>
        <nav class="footer-links" aria-label="Footer">
          <a href="/en/practice-areas">Practice Areas</a>
          <a href="/en/blog">Legal Blog</a>
          <a href="/en/contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    const overlay  = document.getElementById('overlay');
    const menuBtn  = document.getElementById('menuBtn');
    const closeBtn = document.getElementById('closeBtn');
    const backdrop = document.getElementById('overlayBackdrop');
    const navEl    = document.getElementById('mainNav');

    const open  = () => { overlay.classList.add('open'); backdrop.classList.add('visible'); navEl.classList.add('menu-open'); menuBtn.setAttribute('aria-expanded','true'); };
    const close = () => { overlay.classList.remove('open'); backdrop.classList.remove('visible'); navEl.classList.remove('menu-open'); menuBtn.setAttribute('aria-expanded','false'); };

    menuBtn.addEventListener('click', () => overlay.classList.contains('open') ? close() : open());
    closeBtn.addEventListener('click', close);
    backdrop.addEventListener('click', close);
    document.addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Escape' && overlay.classList.contains('open')) close(); });
    document.querySelectorAll('.overlay-nav a').forEach(a => a.addEventListener('click', close));
  </script>

</body>
</html>
